messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com
I pray for deliverance from the stronghold of lust adultery harlotry fornication and pornography I renounce the ways I have used my body to serve my flesh and satan

Thank you for sharing your prayer. It's powerful to renounce those strongholds. If you'd like, I can guide you through specific prayers or resources to support you in this journey. How can I assist you further?
I would appreciate the prayers it seems like the more I want to stop these sins the more intense the temptations are I want to stop these sins permanently

I understand how challenging this can be. Here’s a prayer you can use for deliverance:

"Heavenly Father, we come before your throne room today through the blood of Jesus Christ. We pray against the Spirit of lust, and we renounce all sexual sins that we have been involved in the past, including fornication, masturbation, pornography, and adultery, in the name of Jesus Christ. We break all curses of lust and declare freedom over our lives."

Remember, focusing on Christ and seeking His strength is key. If you need more specific prayers or resources, just let me know!
I would appreciate it pastor I want God but I wanted sin too now I feel there is a stronghold in my life because of how long I have been involved with these sins

It's great that you desire God and recognize the struggle you're facing. It's important to remember that you're not alone in this journey. Here’s a prayer you can use to seek deliverance from that stronghold:

"Heavenly Father, I come before you, acknowledging my struggles and the stronghold of sin in my life. I ask for your forgiveness and cleansing. Help me to turn away from these sins and to seek you wholeheartedly. I renounce the hold that lust, adultery, and pornography have on me. Please break these chains and fill me with your Spirit, guiding me towards healing and freedom in Christ."

Stay focused on seeking Christ, and He will provide the strength you need. If you want more resources or support, feel free to ask!
I want the enemy to release my sexuality and I want deliverance from all sexual addictions and cleansing

It's powerful that you are seeking deliverance and cleansing. Here’s a prayer you can use for that purpose:

"Lord Jesus, I come to you today asking for deliverance from all sexual addictions. I command all spirits of lust, perversion, and any other strongholds to leave me now in the name of Jesus Christ. I renounce the ways I have used my body to serve my flesh and the enemy. I ask for your cleansing and healing in my life. Fill me with your Holy Spirit and help me walk in purity and freedom."

Remember, seeking God and His strength is essential in this process. If you need further support or resources, just let me know!

I ask God forgiveness for fornication I regretted not being married to my wife before sex I renounce that sin I just want it gone so I can be pure in the eyes of God I can't do this in my own strength I'm too weak evil and flawed

It's commendable that you are seeking forgiveness and desiring purity. Here’s a prayer you can use to express your heart to God:

"Heavenly Father, I come before you with a heavy heart, asking for your forgiveness for my sins of fornication. I regret not honoring the sanctity of marriage before engaging in sexual relations. I renounce this sin and ask for your cleansing and healing. I acknowledge my weakness and flaws, and I know I cannot do this on my own. Please fill me with your strength and help me to walk in purity and righteousness in your eyes."

Remember, God is faithful to forgive and restore. If you need more guidance or support, feel free to reach out!
I need my sexuality purified I need my temple cleansed I want to be free from sexual immorality and I repent for not allowing God to lead me so I can lead my wife in a Godly way

It's wonderful that you are seeking purification and a deeper relationship with God. Here’s a prayer you can use to express your desire for cleansing and guidance:

"Lord Jesus, I come to you seeking purification of my sexuality and cleansing of my temple. I repent for allowing sexual immorality to take root in my life and for not allowing you to lead me. I desire to be free from these chains and to lead my wife in a Godly way. Please fill me with your Holy Spirit and guide me in the path of righteousness. Help me to honor you in all aspects of my life and to walk in purity."

Remember, God hears your prayers and desires to help you on this journey. If you need further support or resources, I'm here to assist you!
